  <body>
   <p> This setting will allow to choose sorting order used in Media Item view</p>
    <h1>None</h1> <p>Order is defined by library definition on the NED server</p>
    <h1>by Name</h1> <p>Items are sorted by title<p>
    <h1>by Type</h1> <p>Items are sorted by media type. Videos, Audio, Images, Text<p>
    <h1>byNameAndType</h1><p>This combines previous two methods. Items are sorted by type and by name</p>
